nd could explain why most of them are reliant on their vison without the need for echolocation. (Folia Morphol 2022; 81, 3: 715\u2013722)", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Peter-Ajuzie, I. K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nwaogu, I. C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Majesty-Alukagberie, L. O.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ajaebili, A. C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Farrag, F. A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kassab, M. A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Morsy, K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Abumandour, M.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ec18153144974ab9ef343f99e1fe7402", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/7e6677b4cb340b447a82893d0a3e81ce849d71c5755d78fec6299c95094e7572", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/MU6YRCXE", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/MU6YRCXE", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/cbd94a6ebbe1694c9db5fb6809ac77c6!/b276941-279423", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "715-722", "title": "Folia Morphologica", "volume": "81"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/ec18153144974ab9ef343f99e1fe7402"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:ite